	["You found an ancient artifact. Report to Astral Janus."] = "Znalazles pradawny artefakt. Wroc teraz do janusza gwiezdnego.",
	["So you would like to know the password? I can {reveal} it for a small fee of 15 coins. I really need that gold converter.."] = "Moge sprzedac Ci to haslo za 15 coinow. Potrzebuje pieniedzy na nowy konwerter do monet..",
